data.description: Gaze upon 112 Pinecrest Circle. This hidden gem is tucked away in a wooded cul de sac on a massive 1.89 acres. Whether you're a family looking to settle down in a tranquil setting or an investor looking for an ideal project, this is the property for you. You'll rarely find an all-brick home with so much character. (Listed $20,000 under appraised value) While approaching the property you'll notice the inviting front yard with an extensive driveway. The home comprises 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, & a bonus room on the main level paired with a full basement/ensuite. There are three options to enter the property via the front door, carport, & rear entrance to the basement. As you enter the property, you'll find a quaint dining room off to the right that is perfect for hosting. The home then opens up to a spacious living room & kitchen. The highlight of the living room is the hearty all brick fireplace and shelving perfect for decor or the savvy reader's book collection. The elongated kitchen has plenty of cabinet and counter space for a chef. You'll also find newly purchased stainless steel appliances in this adorable kitchen. The primary suite and secondary rooms are extremely spacious with ample closet space. If you want to enjoy nature you can sit on the cozy deck with steps that provide access to the lower level. Whether you enter from the main or lower level, experience the spacious basement that provides a great escape into solitude. The backyard certainly adds to the value of the property. A large portion of the backyard is cleared allowing you to use it for hosting events, extending the home, outdoor sports, bonfires, etc. The property is shrouded with beautiful trees that maintain an unmatched view of nature. NO HOA ** Note you'll find 2 story new construction properties being built across the street! ** Don't miss out, we welcome you to visit today!!!
